{"translationLines":[{"lineNumber":171681,"originalJapaneseLine":"　本当に人望のない奴め」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Truly a man without any popularity.\""},{"lineNumber":171682,"originalJapaneseLine":"「恐怖で従わせているだけだからな」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"He's only making them obey through fear.\""},{"lineNumber":171683,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ある意味、哀れな男だ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"In a way, he's a pitiful man...\""},{"lineNumber":171684,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ぐっ……！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Guh...!\""},{"lineNumber":171685,"originalJapaneseLine":"骸骨王モドカタがその場に崩れ落ちる。","translatedEnglishLine":"The Skeleton King Modokata collapsed right there."},{"lineNumber":171686,"originalJapaneseLine":"「がははは、俺様の勝ちー！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Gahahaha, I win!\""},{"lineNumber":171687,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……ふっ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Hmph."},{"lineNumber":171688,"originalJapaneseLine":"　なんたる強さ、人とは思えん」","translatedEnglishLine":"What strength, I can't believe he's human.\""},{"lineNumber":171689,"originalJapaneseLine":"ボロボロの身でありながら、","translatedEnglishLine":"Though he was battered and worn,"},{"lineNumber":171690,"originalJapaneseLine":"モドカタは、くつくつと総身を震わせた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Modokata chuckled quietly, trembling all over."},{"lineNumber":171691,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ほう、笑い方を知っていたか……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Oh, so you know how to laugh...\""},{"lineNumber":171692,"originalJapaneseLine":"「笑ってるの初めて見たな……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"This is the first time I've seen you laugh...\""},{"lineNumber":171693,"originalJapaneseLine":"「主らになら……できるかも知れぬな……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Perhaps to you masters... it might be possible...\""},{"lineNumber":171694,"originalJapaneseLine":"「門番である我を倒したのだ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"You have defeated me, the gatekeeper."},{"lineNumber":171695,"originalJapaneseLine":"　通れ」","translatedEnglishLine":"Pass through.\""},{"lineNumber":171696,"originalJapaneseLine":"「お、素直じゃないか」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Oh, you're being obedient.\""},{"lineNumber":171697,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……元より、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...From the start,"},{"lineNumber":171698,"originalJapaneseLine":"　悪鬼に義理立てする筋合いなどなし」","translatedEnglishLine":"I have no reason to be loyal to demons.\""},{"lineNumber":171699,"originalJapaneseLine":"「主らにあの暴虐の化身が殺せるか……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Whether you masters can kill that embodiment of cruelty..."},{"lineNumber":171700,"originalJapaneseLine":"　高みの見物をさせてもらう」","translatedEnglishLine":"I'll watch the show from above.\""},{"lineNumber":171701,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ランス様、また大きな扉がありますよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Lord Rance, there's another large door.\""},{"lineNumber":171702,"originalJapaneseLine":"「む、ついにケイブリスの部屋に着いたか？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm, have we finally reached Kaiburris's room?\""},{"lineNumber":171703,"originalJapaneseLine":"「いや、違うと思う」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"No, I don't think so.\""},{"lineNumber":171704,"originalJapaneseLine":"「何故、分かる？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"How do you know?\""},{"lineNumber":171705,"originalJapaneseLine":"「恐瘴気の濃さだ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"It's the density of the fear miasma."},{"lineNumber":171706,"originalJapaneseLine":"　本物のケイブリスがいるなら、","translatedEnglishLine":"If the real Kaiburris were here,"},{"lineNumber":171707,"originalJapaneseLine":"　こんなもんでは済まない」","translatedEnglishLine":"it wouldn't be this mild.\""},{"lineNumber":171708,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……とりあえず開けてみるか」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...For now, let's try opening it.\""},{"lineNumber":171709,"originalJapaneseLine":"巨大な扉を力を込めて開けてみると、","translatedEnglishLine":"They put strength into opening the huge door,"},{"lineNumber":171710,"originalJapaneseLine":"目の前は洞窟となっていた。","translatedEnglishLine":"and in front was a cave."},{"lineNumber":171711,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あれ？　洞窟だと？","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Huh? A cave?"},{"lineNumber":171712,"originalJapaneseLine":"　まさか道に迷ったのか？」","translatedEnglishLine":"Did we get lost?\""},{"lineNumber":171713,"originalJapaneseLine":"「いや、大丈夫、ケイブリスには近づいている」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"No, it's alright, we're getting closer to Kaiburris.\""},{"lineNumber":171714,"originalJapaneseLine":"「恐瘴気が……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"The fear miasma...\""},

{"lineNumber":171715,"originalJapaneseLine":"「は、はい……一段と……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Y-yes... It's gotten even more..."},

{"lineNumber":171716,"originalJapaneseLine":"　濃くなりましたね……」","translatedEnglishLine":"dense...\""},{"lineNumber":171717,"originalJapaneseLine":"「シャングリラでの恐瘴気なんて、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"The fear miasma in Shangri-La is nothing,"},{"lineNumber":171718,"originalJapaneseLine":"　これに比べれば屁みたいなもんだな……」","translatedEnglishLine":"compared to this, it's just a fart...\""},{"lineNumber":171719,"originalJapaneseLine":"「これが本物の","translatedEnglishLine":"\"This is the real"},{"lineNumber":171720,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ケイブリスが放つ恐瘴気ってわけだ」","translatedEnglishLine":"fear miasma emitted by Kaiburris.\""},{"lineNumber":171721,"originalJapaneseLine":"「数千年、殺戮の世界に生きてきた","translatedEnglishLine":"\"For thousands of years, having lived in a world of slaughter,"},{"lineNumber":171722,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ケイブリスはその存在そのものが暴力と死だ」","translatedEnglishLine":"Kaiburris's very existence is violence and death.\""},{"lineNumber":171723,"originalJapaneseLine":"「常人なら近づくだけで死ぬと言われる……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ordinary people say you die just by getting close...\""},{"lineNumber":171724,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ちっ、俺ですらしんどいぞ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Tch, even I am having a hard time."},{"lineNumber":171725,"originalJapaneseLine":"　より気を引き締め直した方が良さそうだ」","translatedEnglishLine":"We should tighten our concentration even more.\""},{"lineNumber":171726,"originalJapaneseLine":"…………","translatedEnglishLine":"........"},{"lineNumber":171727,"originalJapaneseLine":"……","translatedEnglishLine":"..."},{"lineNumber":171728,"originalJapaneseLine":"恐瘴気の影響で★ランク２０以下のキャラは","translatedEnglishLine":"Due to the influence of the fear miasma, characters below ★ Rank 20"},{"lineNumber":171729,"originalJapaneseLine":"行動不能になりました。","translatedEnglishLine":"are unable to act."},{"lineNumber":171730,"originalJapaneseLine":"ケイブリスの昔話はまだ続いていた。","translatedEnglishLine":"The old tale of Kaiburris continued."},{"lineNumber":171731,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ふう、もう結構話したな。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Phew, we've talked quite a bit already."},{"lineNumber":171732,"originalJapaneseLine":"　あー、どこまで話したっけか……」","translatedEnglishLine":"Ah, where did we leave off...?\""},{"lineNumber":171733,"originalJapaneseLine":"「魔王ナイチサの時代まで、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Up to the era of Demon Lord Naichisa,"},{"lineNumber":171734,"originalJapaneseLine":"　シャリエラ聞きました」","translatedEnglishLine":"I heard from Shariera.\""},{"lineNumber":171735,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おお、そうだそうだ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Oh, right, right."},{"lineNumber":171736,"originalJapaneseLine":"　なら、次は魔王ジルの時代だな」","translatedEnglishLine":"Then next is the era of Demon Lord Jill.\""},{"lineNumber":171737,"originalJapaneseLine":"「魔王ジルが君臨する時代となると、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"When Demon Lord Jill ruled,"},{"lineNumber":171738,"originalJapaneseLine":"　俺様もすげぇー成長していた」","translatedEnglishLine":"I had grown tremendously."},{"lineNumber":171739,"originalJapaneseLine":"「なんたって魔人の中でもトップクラス、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"After all, among demons, I was top class,"},{"lineNumber":171740,"originalJapaneseLine":"　四天王の末席よ」","translatedEnglishLine":"the junior seat of the Four Heavenly Kings.\""}]}

